  <p class="section-desc">Don't have raw returns data? Estimate beta using the shortcut formula: β = (σ_stock / σ_market) × ρ, where σ is standard deviation and ρ is the correlation coefficient.</p>

  <div class="calc-grid">
    <div class="calc-panel">
      <h3>⚡ Quick Estimate Inputs</h3>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="quick-stock-sd">Stock Std Deviation (%)</label>
